JSON webservice for Helga-O web results.

Add a file json-config.php:
<?php

$dsn = "mysql:host=localhost;dbname=<>";
$username = "<>";
$password = "<>";

?>


Example:

{
    "date": "2014-10-25T10:05:13+02:00",
